cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.PE

This paper discusses wireless power transfer (WPT) technology for Internet of Things (IoT) devices, which involves communication and networking aspects (cs.IT), as well as control and optimization (cs.MA, cs.SY). The paper also focuses on scheduling algorithms for multiple users (cs.NI) and power efficiency (cs.PE).
